361
00:26:17,451 --> 00:26:18,744
KANG SI-WOO
HANKUK UNIVERSITY, MECHANICAL ENGINEERING

362
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:20,538
KANG SI-WOO
NO POSTS

363
